long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
::: IMPORTANT NOTICES :::

Thinreports Editor will be released as a desktop application since 0.10.0 following the end of ChromeApps. You can download the latest version from the following page:
https://github.com/thinreports/thinreports-editor/releases

:::

Thinreports is an open source report generation tool for Ruby. This is the official report designer for it. Please see the Thinreports official site (http://www.thinreports.org) or official GitHub project (https://github.com/thinreports/thinreports).
---
Thinreports の公式デザインツールです。詳細は Thinreports の公式サイト (http://www.thinreports.org) 又は公式 GitHub プロジェクト (https://github.com/thinreports/thinreports) をご覧ください。
